title: The Fragrance of the Heart - GlasMagasinet
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Indian, International, Western, Delivery, Take-out
description: Younger sister cafe of The Fragrance of the Heart by the city hall. Nice interior and peaceful environment. Serves similar food to the other cafe, with some prices slightly higher here due to the location. Try the soups and curry. Made in-house Italian ice cream.
